dct_title_s: Central Philippines 1:25,000 / prepared under the direction of the Chief of Engineers, by the Army Map Service (SN), U.S. Army
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by form lines at approximately 50 foot interval and spot heights. Underwater features shown by coral or rock reef drawings. Depth shown by bathymetric isolines in soundings. Shows six classes of roads or trails, railroads, areas of vegetation and cultivation. Includes index to boundaries, coverage diagram, and index to adjoining sheets.
